== About me
I am a final-year PhD student at Peking University (PKU), working with Professors [https://scholar.google.com/citations?hl=zh-CN&user=mOnHMX8AAAAJ&view_op=list_works Zhisheng Duan] and [https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Jinzhi-Wang-2 Jinzhi Wang]. From Dec 2024 to Nov 2025, I was fortunate to work as a visiting PhD at Nanyang Technological University (NTU), Singapore, with Professor [https://francoisgaybalmaz.github.io/ Fran√ßois Gay-Balmaz]. Prior to that, I received my B.Sc.~in Mathematics from Beijing Institute of Technology (BIT) in 2021 under the supervision of Professor [https://scholar.google.com/citations?hl=zh-CN&user=szJq95oAAAAJ&view_op=list_works Donghua Shi]. \n




== Research Interest
My research interest lies at geometric modeling and control of robotic and mechanical systems, which includes the following topics:\n
- *Geometric Mechanics & Control* (especially stochastic & nonholonomic parts)\n
- *Structure-Preserving Discretization* (variational integrators for ODEs/PDEs)\n
- *Geometric Estimation and Filtering* (for robot systems & flexible systems)\n
- *Physics-Informed Learning on Manifolds* (for robotic and mechanical systems)\n






